OL,3,CEx-restaurant boss used #12k of Covid
OL,4,Cloans to buy jewellery
OL,6,FA former restaurant director splurged
OL,7,Fmore than #12,000 of taxpayers' money
OL,8,Fon jewellery after fraudulently
OL,9,Fobtaining two Government loans during
OL,10,Fthe Covid pandemic.JSehrish Yasmin
OL,11,Fapplied for two loans totalling
OL,12,F#100,000 for her company Manny Steak
OL,13,FHouse Ltd - despite businesses only
OL,14,Fbeing entitled to a single loan under
OL,15,Fthe rules of the scheme.JThe 32-year-
OL,16,Fold first applied for #50,000 from the
OL,17,Fon behalf of the company in May 2020.
