OL,3,CEx-restaurant boss used #12k of Covid
OL,4,Cloans to buy jewellery
OL,6,FShe then secured a second #50,000 loan
OL,7,Ffor the same company, which traded as
OL,8,FToro's Steakhouse on Wilmslow Road, ,
OL,9,Fsouth Manchester, just one month later.
OL,11,FYasmin, who is also a qualified nurse,
OL,12,Fthen proceeded to spend more than
OL,13,F#12,000 in the Jewellery Quarter in
OL,14,FBirmingham with the funds, heard.
OL,16,FLast week Yasmin, of Grasmere Road,
OL,17,FCheadle, Greater Manchester, was
OL,18,Fsentenced to 10 months in prison,
OL,19,Fsuspended for 12 months.
