OL,3,CEx-restaurant boss used #12k of Covid
OL,4,Cloans to buy jewellery
OL,6,FDuring a sentencing hearing on 16 May,
OL,7,FYasmin, who has now paid the two loans
OL,8,Fback in full, was also ordered to pay
OL,9,Fcosts and compensation totalling
OL,10,F#5,000 within 28 days.
OL,12,FThe Government's Bounce Back Loan
OL,13,FScheme was launched to enable smaller
OL,14,Fbusinesses to access finance more
OL,15,Fquickly during the coronavirus
OL,16,Fpandemic. Money from the loan could
OL,17,Falso only be used for the economic
OL,18,Fbenefit of the business, not for
OL,19,Fpersonal purposes.
