OL,4,Cloans to buy jewellery
OL,6,FYasmin should have started repaying
OL,7,Feach loan one year after she received
OL,8,Fthe funds in 2020, but only started to
OL,9,Fdo so once Insolvency Service
OL,10,Finvestigations began in December 2022,
OL,11,Fthe court heard.JShe committed a
OL,12,Ffurther offence when Manny Steak House
OL,13,FLtd was liquidated in May 2021 by not
OL,14,Fdelivering books and records to the
OL,15,Fliquidator when requested.JDavid
OL,16,FSnasdell, chief investigator at the
OL,17,FInsolvency Service, said: "Bounce Back
OL,18,FLoans were introduced by the
OL,19,Fgovernment to help small and medium-
OL,20,Fsized businesses survive during the
OL,21,FCovid pandemic.
