OL,3,CEx-restaurant boss used #12k of Covid
OL,4,Cloans to buy jewellery
OL,6,F"Sehrish Yasmin exploited this
OL,7,Ftaxpayer-backed scheme by applying for
OL,8,Ftwo loans when businesses were only
OL,9,Fentitled to one and compounded this by
OL,10,Fspending significant sums on jewellery.
OL,12,F"While we are of course pleased that
OL,13,FYasmin has finally acknowledged her
OL,14,Fwrongdoing and repaid the two loans in
OL,15,Ffull, we are disappointed that this
OL,16,Fonly happened following our extensive
OL,17,Finvestigations into her fraudulent
OL,18,Factivities."JAttempts have been made
OL,19,Fto contact Yasmin for comment.
